&lt;p&gt;AI Platform builds and operates the LLM and agent infrastructure every team at Coinbase builds on, and ships high impact AI agents on top of it. We are the company&#39;s single path to LLMs and the substrate for the full agent lifecycle: build, deploy, run, observe, improve.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;LLM Gateway: one API for 60+ models across all major providers, including self hosted open weight models, with auth, PII redaction, quotas, fallbacks, and cost optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI Hub: single front door for agents, skills, MCP servers, knowledge bases, models, memories, and keys&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agent and MCP runtime: microVM sandboxes per agent run, a governed MCP gateway over 125+ servers, cross trust agent identity, tier 1 agents for code, analytics, and exec personas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge Bases: connect any data source, auto provision vector and markdown stores, queryable by any agent over MCP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AI Spend Hub: FinOps for AI, spend attribution and governance across the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluation and observability: in house LLM as judge harness with full tracing and eval tooling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company wide chat and low code workflow surfaces, thousands of weekly actives each&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Applied AI: we embed with teams to build production agents, build the feedback loops that let subject matter experts refine them, and apply traditional ML including fine tuning where it beats prompting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilizes and builds generative AI responsibly, maintaining human oversight to deliver business-ready outputs and drive measurable improvements in workflow efficiency, cost, and quality&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
